sequenceDiagram
    participant A as agent
    participant T as search_hybrid tool
    participant S as search_hybrid()
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant R as rerank_results()
    participant M as ToolMessage / state

    A->>T: Tool call with query, BM25 keywords, country, rerank context
    T->>T: Normalize country_code
    T->>S: Run hybrid target retrieval
    S->>DB: Profile vector + BM25 query
    S->>DB: Product vector + BM25 query
    DB-->>S: Candidate target rows
    S-->>R: shortlist with products_services
    R->>R: LLM keep/discard batches
    R->>DB: Load deals, funds, shareholdings
    DB-->>R: Deal and acquirer evidence
    R-->>T: Final result payload
    T-->>M: ToolMessage artifact and Command update
    M-->>A: Final answer mode
